  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "The world’s leading companies trust Hazelcast to modernize applications and take instant action on data in motion to create new revenue streams, mitigate risk, and operate more efficiently. Businesses use Hazelcast’s unified **real-time data platform** to process **streaming** data, enrich it with historical context and take instant action with standard or **ML/AI-driven automation** - before it is stored in a database or data lake.",
